<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٣٥٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6307">مُغِيرَةُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ الْقُرَشِيُّ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3645">أَبِي الزِّنَادِ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3424">الْأَعْرَجِ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> <span class="c2">«اخْتَتَنَ إِبْرَاهِيمُ <span class="special">﵇</span> وَهْوَ ابْنُ ثَمَانِينَ سَنَةً بِالْقَدُّومِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>